low = -2.0
high = 2.0
base_estimator = ExtraTreesRegressor(random_state=2)
opt = Optimizer([(low, high), (low + 4, high + 4)], base_estimator,
    n_initial_points=1, acq_optimizer='sampling')
assert_raises(ValueError, opt.tell, [(high + 0.5, high + 0.5), (high + 0.5,
    high + 0.5)], [2.0, 3.0])
assert_raises(ValueError, opt.tell, [(low - 0.5, high + 0.5), (low - 0.5, 
    high + 0.5)], [2.0, 3.0])
pytest.mark.fast_test
